            <title>[LU-11645] Fix sanity-sec test 31</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11645</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In sanity-sec test 31, the command to add a new LNet network ${NETTYPE}999&lt;br/&gt;
may fail if the servers or other clients have an interface name different from the one used&lt;br/&gt;
on the client running the test.&lt;br/&gt;
It is necessary to execute the command directly on the remote nodes with do_nodes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
